name: L A B E L S
description:
Brown, manila paper, luggage style labels featuring folded 3D origami birds made from beautiful vintage maps & papers.

Each label is hand made by re-cycling vintage books & papers, making each one completely unique.

Available in a mixed pack of 6, as pictured, made from beautiful vintage children's books, old wrapping papers, vintage dressmaking patterns, and maps among other things. Or also available is a pack of 6 'MAP' only labels. The labels come strung and measure approximately 9cm x 4.5cm

Due to their hand made nature, please expect slight differences and the tiniest of imperfections between products...they were made with 
L O V E in Clerkenwell, London.

name: S C A L L O P
description:
Infant Art Club 'SCALLOP' design decorative garlands available in primary colour way as well as plain black, navy, white or red. Made with  150g/m2 card, sewn together in semi circles measuring approximately 5cm across. The total length of each garland is approximately 4m.

Infant Art Club Garlands are made using specially selected papers and are ideal for decorating your everyday living space as well as special occasions. They can also make unique gift and beautiful alternatives to greeting cards. 

Due to their hand made nature, please expect slight differences and the tiniest of imperfections between products...they were hand cut and strung for you with L O V E in Clerkenwell, London :-)

Decoration for life (or just for Christmas).
